description: Marian was visiting his aunt in Prague. I met him near her house when he went for a little walk. The guy was cute and talkative. I liked his cheerful attitude and hoped that things would go well. Marian certainly liked money because he didn't think twice about my offers. He just wanted to hide a bit so his aunty couldn't see him. We hid behind trees and played with each other. The guy looked very innocent but was a fast learner. I deepthroated him a little and then turned my attention to his beautifully shaved asshole. I drilled him like there was no tomorrow, fully aware of that I might never see the boy again. He struggled but had a great time in the end. To my surprise, he was quite enthusiastic about meeting again. I got his number so if you want to see more of him, let me know.
title: Czech Hunter 457
